descriptionHtml:
Get more out of your workplace with Envoy. Manage your upcoming visitors and invite new guests, get notified about incoming packages, book nearby conference rooms, and more. Tap into Envoy’s workplace platform (Visitors, Deliveries, and Rooms) from one intuitive app. If your office uses Envoy, the Envoy app will help you focus on the work that matters most.

INVITE VISITORS & GET NOTIFIED WHEN THEY ARRIVE

Invite guests to your office and keep track of who is scheduled to arrive when, so you’re prepared for every visit. Choose how you’d like to be notified when visitors arrive to see you.

KEEP TRACK OF YOUR IMPORTANT DELIVERIES

Simply snap a picture to automatically log deliveries, notify each recipient, and send reminders to make sure packages get picked up. Recipients get notified as soon as a package arrives and can easily confirm pick-up.

QUICKLY BOOK A ROOM FOR LAST-MINUTE MEETINGS

If you’re on the go and need a room, get room recommendations based on your location. Book a nearby space in one click.

When you visit other offices that use Envoy, sign-in will go from easy to effortless:

SIGN-IN IN SECONDS

If you visit an office that uses Envoy, the Envoy app will automatically send your details directly to the iPad so you can sign-in easily and collect a stamp for each office visit.

Register to come into the office, reserve a desk for the day, manage your upcoming visitors, get notified about incoming packages, book nearby conference rooms, and more. Tap into Envoy’s workplace platform (Protect, Visitors, Deliveries, Rooms, and Desks) from one intuitive app.

RESERVE A SPOT IN THE OFFICE

Get cleared to work in the office each day by completing a health questionnaire. Once you arrive, reduce the spread of germs with a touchless sign-in using the Envoy Mobile app.

EASILY FIND AND BOOK A DESK FOR THE DAY

Once you’re approved to come on-site, automatically book a desk for the day to make sure you have a safe space to work. Change up where you sit each day to collaborate with different teammates or gain a fresh perspective.

INVITE VISITORS & GET NOTIFIED WHEN THEY ARRIVE

Invite guests to your office and keep track of who is scheduled to arrive when, so you’re prepared for every visit. Choose how you’d like to be notified when visitors arrive to see you.

KEEP TRACK OF YOUR IMPORTANT DELIVERIES

Simply snap a picture to automatically log deliveries, notify each recipient, and send reminders to make sure packages get picked up. Recipients get notified as soon as a package arrives and can easily confirm pick-up.

BOOK A ROOM FOR LAST-MINUTE MEETINGS

If you’re on the go and need a room, get room recommendations based on your location. Book a nearby space in one click.

RESERVE A SPOT IN THE OFFICE

EASILY FIND AND BOOK A DESK FOR THE DAY

INVITE VISITORS & GET NOTIFIED WHEN THEY ARRIVE

Invite guests to your office and keep track of who is scheduled to arrive when, so you’re prepared for every visit. Choose how you’d like to be notified when visitors arrive to see you.

BOOK A ROOM FOR LAST-MINUTE MEETINGS

If you’re on the go and need a room, get room recommendations based on your location. Book a nearby space in one click.

title: Envoy

creator: Envoy, Inc.
descriptionHtml:
Make your workplace work better for you with Envoy. Coordinate your office schedule with coworkers, see where to go with workplace maps, reserve the perfect desk, book a nearby conference room, invite visitors, get notified about packages, report workplace issues, and more.

COORDINATE YOUR OFFICE SCHEDULE
Set your schedule for hybrid work. Easily see who plans to work onsite each day so you can plan to be there too. Invite coworkers to join you in person for collaborative work.

NAVIGATE WITH INTERACTIVE WORKPLACE MAPS
Know where to go and who to meet in the office. Find where your coworkers are sitting, book meeting rooms, see visitor details, and know where to pick up deliveries–all from the interactive workplace map.

EASILY BOOK THE PERFECT DESK
Book a desk by the hour, day, or week. Find a desk with the amenities you need to be comfortable and productive in the workplace. Save a spot by your team, favorite coworkers, or key collaborators to get things done.

BOOK A ROOM FOR LAST-MINUTE MEETINGS
Easily find the closest available meeting room on the interactive workplace map, so you can book a space, even when you’re on the go. Check in to your next meeting right from your phone, or free up the room for someone else.

INVITE VISITORS & GET NOTIFIED WHEN THEY ARRIVE
Invite guests to your office and keep track of who is scheduled to arrive and when, so you’re prepared for every visit. Receive a notification when your visitor arrives so your guest is never kept waiting.

KEEP TRACK OF YOUR DELIVERIES
Get notified as soon as your package arrives and easily confirm once you’ve picked it up, so you feel confident getting mail delivered to work.

REPORT WORKPLACE ISSUES
Create tickets right on your phone, including taking photos and noting the location of issues in the moment, so your facilities and IT teams can resolve them quickly.

CERTIFY THAT YOU’RE HEALTHY
Get cleared to work onsite by submitting proof of vaccination or completing a health check. Once you arrive, reduce the spread of germs with a touchless sign-in using the Envoy mobile app.

title: Envoy

creator: Envoy, Inc.
descriptionHtml:
Make your workplace work better for you with Envoy. Coordinate your office schedule with coworkers, see where to go with workplace maps, reserve the perfect desk, book a nearby conference room, invite visitors, get notified about packages, report workplace issues, and more.

COORDINATE YOUR OFFICE SCHEDULE
Set your schedule for hybrid work. Easily see who plans to work onsite each day so you can plan to be there too. Invite coworkers to join you in person for collaborative work.

NAVIGATE WITH INTERACTIVE WORKPLACE MAPS
Know where to go and who to meet in the office. Find where your coworkers are sitting, book meeting rooms, see visitor details, and know where to pick up deliveries–all from the interactive workplace map.

EASILY BOOK THE PERFECT DESK
Book a desk by the hour, day, or week. Find a desk with the amenities you need to be comfortable and productive in the workplace. Save a spot by your team, favorite coworkers, or key collaborators to get things done.

BOOK A ROOM FOR LAST-MINUTE MEETINGS
Easily find the closest available meeting room on the interactive workplace map, so you can book a space, even when you’re on the go. Check in to your next meeting right from your phone, or free up the room for someone else.

INVITE VISITORS & GET NOTIFIED WHEN THEY ARRIVE
Invite guests to your office and keep track of who is scheduled to arrive and when, so you’re prepared for every visit. Receive a notification when your visitor arrives so your guest is never kept waiting.

KEEP TRACK OF YOUR DELIVERIES
Get notified as soon as your package arrives and easily confirm once you’ve picked it up, so you feel confident getting mail delivered to work.

REPORT WORKPLACE ISSUES
Create tickets right on your phone, including taking photos and noting the location of issues in the moment, so your facilities and IT teams can resolve them quickly.

CERTIFY THAT YOU’RE HEALTHY
Get cleared to work onsite by submitting proof of vaccination or completing a health check. Once you arrive, reduce the spread of germs with a touchless sign-in using the Envoy mobile app.

Make your workplace work better for you with Envoy. Coordinate your office schedule with coworkers, see where to go with workplace maps, reserve the perfect desk, book a nearby conference room, invite visitors, get notified about packages, report workplace issues, and more.

COORDINATE YOUR OFFICE SCHEDULE
Set your schedule for hybrid work. Easily see who plans to work onsite each day so you can plan to be there too. Invite coworkers to join you in person for collaborative work.

NAVIGATE WITH INTERACTIVE WORKPLACE MAPS
Know where to go and who to meet in the office. Find where your coworkers are sitting, book meeting rooms, see visitor details, and know where to pick up deliveries–all from the interactive workplace map.

EASILY BOOK THE PERFECT DESK
Book a desk by the hour, day, or week. Find a desk with the amenities you need to be comfortable and productive in the workplace. Save a spot by your team, favorite coworkers, or key collaborators to get things done.

BOOK A ROOM FOR LAST-MINUTE MEETINGS
Easily find the closest available meeting room on the interactive workplace map, so you can book a space, even when you’re on the go. Check in to your next meeting right from your phone, or free up the room for someone else.

INVITE VISITORS & GET NOTIFIED WHEN THEY ARRIVE
Invite guests to your office and keep track of who is scheduled to arrive and when, so you’re prepared for every visit. Receive a notification when your visitor arrives so your guest is never kept waiting.

KEEP TRACK OF YOUR DELIVERIES
Get notified as soon as your package arrives and easily confirm once you’ve picked it up, so you feel confident getting mail delivered to work.

REPORT WORKPLACE ISSUES
Create tickets right on your phone, including taking photos and noting the location of issues in the moment, so your facilities and IT teams can resolve them quickly.

CERTIFY THAT YOU’RE HEALTHY
Get cleared to work onsite by submitting proof of vaccination or completing a health check. Once you arrive, reduce the spread of germs with a touchless sign-in using the Envoy mobile app.
